{"tid":138911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉下午開記招 料宣佈未能入閘出局","createTime":"2017-03-01T03:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T10:19:26.000Z","uid":42804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca0d5b206609102179c2ca375bd1f0a7d80a6d9","tid":138911,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"特首選舉提名期將於今午5時結束，4位宣佈參選的人士中，僅葉劉淑儀至今仍未遞交提名成候選人。葉劉今午2時半將召開記者會，預料將交代在最後關頭，是否取得足夠提名票入閘。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀昨承認，曾有民主派願意幫她找十數張提名，但坦言目前離入閘不只欠「十張八張」。據了解，在西環封殺下，葉劉現時約只有20多個提名，主要是新民黨的24名選委及民主派會計界選委何駿雄，人大代表李少光昨亦承認已提名葉劉，但距離葉劉入閘所需150個入閘提名門檻相距甚遠。如她未能入閘，今次已經是葉劉繼2012年後，再度因未獲足夠提名，未能入閘參選特首。"},{"pid":"d23296bfa8c4cc1fa60fce6bc176df6007c3df37","tid":138911,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"再度未有足夠提名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe72fd7790a74b68a2db103361bb4d5b58a54c0f","tid":138911,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"睇黎一陣又要哭訴下屆再參選<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e0e30cc0b6041c7c5c61186359387401b8f4c0","tid":138911,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"渣ga<br />\n又話戰到一兵一卒"},{"pid":"55f1dba2e07d84593829d0a31c4f8cdab84d10c1","tid":138911,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga<br />\n又話戰到一兵一卒</blockquote><br />\n從來都係一兵一卒架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4daf8dd6f6a2059734d3301d331e667a60ef3d7c","tid":138911,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>渣ga<br />\n又話戰到一兵一卒</blockquote><br />\n從來都係一兵一卒架啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass